            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40809202/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40809202/" class="">最后一页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lnayg1221/" class=" " title="葉紙不會飛">葉紙不會飛</a>
                (嘈嘈切切錯雜彈)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40809202">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">只有战斗中的伙伴才有资格成为和平时期的伙伴。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-12-18 23:00</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                只有战斗中的伙伴才有资格成为和平时期的伙伴。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







